<figureCitation id="47E173F3FF91FF82FF7EFACBFF12FAD9" box="[136,229,1310,1337]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="7.[136,229,926,948]" captionTargetId="figure-15@7.[313,1273,190,902]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 3. The distribution of confirmed specimens of C. brachycarpa." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6580483" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6580483/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="259">Figure 3</figureCitation>
(a–i) in 
<bibRefCitation id="BB4B1287FF91FF82FEC9FACBFDE4FAD8" author="Bacigalupo, N. M." box="[319,531,1310,1336]" pageId="16" pageNumber="259" pagination="377 - 396" refId="ref29687" refString="Bacigalupo, N. M. (1979) El genero Callitriche en la flora argentina. Darwiniana 22: 377 - 396." type="journal article" year="1979">Bacigalupo (1979)</bibRefCitation>
; 
<figureCitation id="47E173F3FF91FF82FDE9FACBFD7CFAD8" box="[543,651,1310,1336]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="4.[136,229,1943,1965]" captionTargetBox="[159,1436,225,1919]" captionTargetId="figure-31@4.[151,1436,190,1919]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 1. Fruits of Callitriche in Oceania and Australasia: a—C. antarctica, b—C. aucklandica, c—C. brachycarpa, d—C. brutia, e—C. capricorni, f—C. chathamensis, g—C. cyclocarpa i face on and ii end on, h—C. cycloptera, i—C. deflexa, j—C. fuliginea." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577540" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6577540/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="259">Figure 1k</figureCitation>
in Lansdown and Hassemer. 
<figureCitation id="47E173F3FF91FF82FC23FACBFBC3FAD8" box="[981,1076,1310,1336]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="17.[136,229,1913,1935]" captionTargetBox="[153,1436,190,1889]" captionTargetId="figure-15@17.[151,1436,190,1889]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="FIGURE 10. Fruits of Callitriche in Oceania and Australasia: a—C. heterophylla, b—C. insularis, c—C. muelleri, d—C. palustris, e—C. papuana, f—C. peploides, g—C. petriei, h—C. platycarpa, i—C. sonderi, j—C. stagnalis, k—C. umbonata." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577553" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6577553/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="259">Fig. 10a</figureCitation>
